CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 29, 1945, pg. 3, reads: "Sixteen Candles - Betty Louise Wade, daughter of Mr. and Mrs. Allen Wade, 401 Robinson Court, celebrated her sixteenth birthday recently with a party. Friends and relatives helped her observe the happy occasion. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Betty Louise Wade standing behind her sixteenth birthday cake, surrounded by young women and men, in Wade home, 401 Robinson Court
